        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <strong>Move</strong>
            </td>
            <td>-</td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <h5>Unit Characteristics</h5>
    <ul>
        <li>Point of entry for all purchased air, land and sea units</li>
        <li>Can produce up to 3 units (-1 per damage taken)</li>
        <li>Can be damaged up to 6 Damage Points. For each damage point it can produce one unit less.</li>
        <li>Can be upgraded to a major one at a cost of 20 IPCs (only on original controlled territories with an IPC value of 3 or higher)</li>
        <li>Can only be placed on controlled territories with an IPC value of 2 or higher</li>
        <li>Can not be placed on an Island</li>
    </ul>
{% endblock %}

